Sage observation + correspondence
=================================

runtime_probe.json
  GENERATED live dump (category_sample + super_categories).
  Rebuild: `sage -python -m sage_category_tree_stubs.runtime_probe`
  or `just manifests-probe`.

observed.json
  GENERATED empirical snapshot = inventory census ⊕ runtime probe.
  Rebuild: `sage -python -m sage_category_tree_stubs.observed_build`
  or via `just manifests` / `just manifests-probe`.
  Does not correct Sage parents; does not store property/structure/stuff.

mapping.yaml
  REVIEWED Sage → normalized correspondence (+ auto unsupported rows
  for unreviewed public categories / edges / axioms / constructions).
  Targets are normalized ids only (cat.*, clf.*, …).
  Pullback expressions live in design/normalized/manifest/, not here.
  Every observed immediate-supercategory edge has exactly one disposition.

correspondence.dot / observed_parents.dot / edge_dispositions.dot
  GENERATED views from the join of the three manifests.
